全球在金融科技的投資從2008年的9.3億美元到2014年的120億美元總共成長了12倍。<ref name="A">{{cite web | url=http://www.accenture.com/Microsites/fsinsights/capital-markets-uk/Documents/Accenture-Global-Boom-in-Fintech-Investment.pdf | title=The Boom in Global Fintech Investment | publisher=Accenture | date=2014 | accessdate=9 December 2014 | archive-date=2015-02-13 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150213060313/http://www.accenture.com/Microsites/fsinsights/capital-markets-uk/Documents/Accenture-Global-Boom-in-Fintech-Investment.pdf | dead-url=no }}</ref>根據倫敦市長辦公室表示：新興的金融科技業在倫敦有著快速成長，我們勞動人口約有40％是在金融業和科技業服務；<ref name="HT">{{cite web | url=http://www.hottopics.ht/stories/fintech/what-is-fintech-and-why-it-matters/ | title=What is FinTech and why does it matter to all entrepreneurs? | publisher=Hot Topics | date=July 2014 | accessdate=9 December 2014 | archive-date=2014-12-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141226063327/http://www.hottopics.ht/stories/fintech/what-is-fintech-and-why-it-matters/ | dead-url=no }}</ref> FundingCircle, Nutmeg 和 TransferWise等公司是比較有名的代表。

